
description
    Remap octave talkers.  Makes the octave up and
    down buttons transpose by a Major 7th instead.

    This script should be run with pico setups only

script
    empty join keygroup 1 listen talker 6 listen
    all phrase cancel
    octave by 0.91666666666666663 when 1 up
    octave by 0.91666666666666663 when 2 down
